## Limitations
This report is based on opinion pieces and statements from individuals and organizations with specific viewpoints. As such, it may not fully represent the diversity of opinions on the topic. Additionally, the report does not delve into the legal intricacies of the Supreme Court's decision-making process or the potential consequences of overturning Roe v. Wade. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the legal and societal implications.

